title: Disarming Wink
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

During a tense situation you may pay ''1x Propriety'' and give someone a disarming wink, triggering them to start trying to placate the situation. It won't change anyone's mind, but will give you an ally in attempting to disarm the situation.